Edge Session UI Requirements

Becoming Protocol --- Arousal Session Interface

Version 2.0 --- January 2026

*Updated with Hypno Collage Layout System*

Executive Summary

This document defines requirements for an immersive edging/gooning
interface that integrates with the existing Becoming Protocol systems:
arousal state tracking, Lovense haptic control, content tiering, arousal
auctions, and feminization conditioning.

The UI should feel like entering a distinct mode---immersive, focused,
psychologically compelling---while being functionally robust for
tracking, control, and post-session evidence capture.

**Key Update (v2.0):** This version introduces the Hypno Collage Layout
System---a multi-column content display inspired by PMV/hypno content
that creates parallel stimulation, cognitive overload, and subliminal
text overlay for deeper trance states and more effective conditioning.

Part 1: Session Types & Entry Points

1.1 Session Type Definitions

  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Type**        **Purpose**            **Frequency**   **Duration**   **Completion**
  --------------- ---------------------- --------------- -------------- -----------------
  **Type A:       Create                 2-3x weekly     20-40 min      Denied
  Anchoring**     feminization-arousal                                  
                  association                                           

  **Type B:       Positive reinforcement 1x weekly max   30-60 min      Allowed (jackpot)
  Reward**        for practice                                          

  **Type C:       Stay in sweet spot     Daily option    10-20 min      Denied
  Maintenance**                                                         

  **Goon          Deep trance-like       Special unlock  45-90 min      AI decides
  Session**       absorption                                            
  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1.2 Entry Requirements

Each session type has specific unlock conditions that integrate with the
ratchet system:

-   **Type A (Anchoring):** Always available. No requirements.

-   **Type B (Reward):** Earned. Requires weekly protocol complete, 5+
    denial days, no edge debt, 7+ days since last Type B.

-   **Type C (Maintenance):** Always available. No requirements.

-   **Goon Session:** Earned. Requires Phase 3+, 20+ sessions completed,
    or special unlock.

1.3 Entry Flow

The session entry flow guides users through configuration with
appropriate friction:

-   Today View тЖТ \"Begin Session\" button

-   Session Type Selection (shows availability, locked states)

-   Pre-Session Check-In (arousal state, content tier, haptic device,
    environment)

-   Session Configuration (target edges, AI control level, content
    layout, time limit)

-   **Content Layout Selection (NEW)**

-   Session Start

Part 2: Hypno Collage Layout System (NEW)

The Hypno Collage Layout System introduces a multi-column content
display that replicates the psychological effects of PMV/hypno content.
This layout creates parallel stimulation that overwhelms the analytical
mind and facilitates deeper trance states.

2.1 Psychological Principles

**Why multi-column works:**

-   **Parallel Stimulation:** Multiple focal points prevent the
    analytical mind from settling on any one thing, facilitating
    trance-like absorption.

-   **Cognitive Overload:** The busy-ness is intentional---it overwhelms
    resistance and conscious filtering.

-   **Subliminal Text Layer:** Phrases appear/disappear faster than
    conscious processing but slower than true subliminal, creating a
    \"can\'t help but read it\" effect.

-   **Sensory Integration:** Combines visual, auditory, and textual
    channels simultaneously for maximum impact.

2.2 Content Layout Modes

  -------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Mode**      **Layout**             **Psychological Effect**
  ------------- ---------------------- ------------------------------------
  **single**    One content piece,     Focused attention, good for
                full screen            beginners

  **dual**      Two columns, split     Divided attention, starting to
                screen                 overwhelm

  **collage**   Three columns, PMV     Full parallel stimulation, cognitive
                style                  overload

  **hypno**     Three columns + rapid  Maximum absorption, trance
                text stream            facilitation

  **minimal**   Content only, no UI    Deep goon mode, zero distractions
  -------------------------------------------------------------------------

2.3 Layout Configuration Interface

type ContentLayoutMode =

\| \'single\' // Traditional single content display

\| \'dual\' // Two-column split

\| \'collage\' // Three-column PMV-style

\| \'hypno\' // Full hypno mode with text stream

\| \'minimal\'; // Goon mode - minimal chrome

interface CollageConfig {

columns: 2 \| 3;

syncTiming: boolean; // Sync transitions across panels

transitionStyle: \'cut\' \| \'fade\' \| \'slide\';

transitionDurationMs: number;

contentMix: ContentMixStrategy;

audioChannel: \'left\' \| \'right\' \| \'center\' \| \'rotate\';

}

2.4 Content Mix Strategies

The collage system can mix content across columns using different
strategies:

-   **homogeneous:** Same category in all columns (e.g., all
    feminization)

-   **complementary:** Related categories that reinforce each other

-   **contrasting:** Different categories for sensory variety

-   **progressive:** Intensity increases left-to-right or over time

-   **ai_curated:** AI selects based on session context and user
    response

Part 3: Text Overlay System (NEW)

The text overlay system displays affirmations, mantras, and conditioning
phrases over the content in a rapid, semi-subliminal manner that mirrors
PMV/hypno content aesthetics.

3.1 Display Timing

interface TextOverlayTiming {

mode: \'subliminal\' \| \'readable\' \| \'lingering\';

// Subliminal: 200-500ms (barely caught)

// Readable: 1000-2000ms (can read, can\'t analyze)

// Lingering: 3000-5000ms (reinforcement style)

displayDurationMs: number;

fadeInMs: number;

fadeOutMs: number;

intervalBetweenMs: { min: number; max: number }; // Variable

}

3.2 Text Positioning

type TextPosition =

\| \'center\' // Center of screen

\| \'per_column\' // Each column gets its own text

\| \'floating\' // Random positions

\| \'stacked\' // Multiple texts visible at once

\| \'edge_anchored\'; // Appears at top/bottom edges

3.3 Typography Styles

interface TextOverlayStyle {

fontFamily: \'elegant\' \| \'minimal\' \| \'bold\' \| \'script\';

// elegant: Playfair Display, Cormorant

// minimal: Inter, system-ui

// bold: Impact, Anton

// script: Great Vibes, Pacifico

color: string; // Usually white or pink

accentColor: string; // For highlighted words

shadowIntensity: number; // 0-1, for readability

glowEffect: boolean; // Soft glow around text

mixBlendMode: \'normal\' \| \'screen\' \| \'overlay\';

}

3.4 Affirmation Pools by Context

The text overlay system draws from context-appropriate affirmation
pools:

  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Pool**            **Example Affirmations**
  ------------------- -------------------------------------------------------
  **feminization**    *\"becoming feminine\", \"she\'s here\", \"this is who
                      you are\", \"feel yourself becoming\"*

  **edge**            *\"hold it\", \"not yet\", \"feel that edge\", \"stay
                      there\", \"good girl, hold\"*

  **recovery**        *\"breathe\", \"good girl\", \"you held so well\",
                      \"rest now\"*

  **identity**        *\"you are her\", \"there\'s no going back\", \"you
                      belong here\"*

  **encouragement**   *\"that\'s it\", \"you\'re doing so well\", \"deeper\",
                      \"let go\"*

  **desire**          *\"crave\", \"want\", \"need\", \"ache for it\", \"you
                      can\'t resist\"*
  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

