4.3 Visual Design Principles

**Immersive Mode Requirements:**

-   Dark theme mandatory (reduces screen glare, focuses attention)

-   Minimal chrome (controls appear on tap, fade when not needed)

-   Content area maximized

-   Subtle ambient animations (breathing pulses, soft glows)

-   No jarring transitions between content pieces

-   **(NEW)** Seamless column transitions with optional sync

Color System

:root {

\--bg-session: #0a0a0a;

\--text-primary: #ffffff;

\--text-muted: #666666;

\--accent-arousal: #ff4d6d; /\* Pink/red \*/

\--accent-affirm: #c77dff; /\* Purple for affirmations \*/

\--accent-edge: #ff6b6b; /\* Red pulse for edge \*/

\--accent-calm: #4ecdc4; /\* Teal for breathe/calm \*/

\--accent-denial: #ffd93d; /\* Gold for control \*/

\--overlay-text: #ffffff; /\* NEW: Text overlay \*/

\--overlay-accent: #ff9ec4; /\* NEW: Highlighted words \*/

}

Part 5: Content Column System (NEW)

5.1 Column Configuration

interface ContentColumn {

id: string;

position: \'left\' \| \'center\' \| \'right\';

// Content source

contentQueue: SessionContent\[\];

currentContent: SessionContent \| null;

// Timing

transitionIntervalMs: { min: number; max: number };

lastTransition: Date;

// Per-column text overlay

textOverlay: {

enabled: boolean;

pool: string\[\]; // Affirmation pool for this column

position: \'top\' \| \'center\' \| \'bottom\';

currentText: string \| null;

};

// Audio routing

audioEnabled: boolean;

audioPan: number; // -1 (left) to 1 (right)

}

5.2 Synchronization Modes

Columns can be synchronized in various ways for different psychological
effects:

type SyncMode =

\| \'independent\' // Each column transitions on its own schedule

\| \'synchronized\' // All columns transition together

\| \'cascade\' // LeftтЖТCenterтЖТRight with 500ms delay

\| \'random\'; // Occasional sync, mostly independent

5.3 Content Cycling Logic

interface ContentCycleConfig {

// Timing variability (prevents habituation)

baseIntervalMs: number; // Base time between transitions

variationPercent: number; // ┬▒% randomization

// Intensity escalation

speedUpOverSession: boolean; // Transitions get faster

speedUpFactor: number; // How much faster per edge

minIntervalMs: number; // Floor (don\'t go faster than this)

// Content selection

avoidRecentCount: number; // Don\'t repeat last N items

weightByEngagement: boolean; // Favor content user responds to

tierProgression: boolean; // Increase tier as session progresses

}

Part 6: Edge Tracking Interface

6.1 Edge Button Behavior

interface EdgeAction {

onTap: () =\> {

incrementEdgeCount();

triggerHapticPulse(\'edge_reached\');

showEdgeConfirmation();

logEdgeTimestamp();

checkForAuctionTrigger();

updateIntensityDisplay();

// NEW: Collage mode enhancements

if (layoutMode === \'collage\' \|\| layoutMode === \'hypno\') {

triggerSynchronizedFlash(); // All columns flash

showCenteredAffirmation(); // \"Good girl\" center screen

speedUpContentCycle(); // Faster after edge

}

},

feedback: {

haptic: \'strong_pulse\',

visual: \'ripple_expand\',

audio: \'subtle_chime\',

duration: 500

}

}

6.2 Edge Data Capture

interface EdgeEvent {

id: string;

sessionId: string;

edgeNumber: number;

timestamp: Date;

timeFromSessionStart: number; // seconds

timeSinceLastEdge: number; // seconds

intensityAtEdge: number; // 0-20 (from haptic)

hapticPatternActive: string;

// NEW: Collage mode data

layoutMode: ContentLayoutMode;

contentDisplayed: {

column1?: string; // Content ID

column2?: string;

column3?: string;

};

textOverlayActive: string \| null; // What affirmation was showing

auctionTriggered: boolean;

notes?: string;

}

6.3 Recovery Period (Updated for Collage)

interface RecoveryPeriod {

minDuration: 15; // seconds

maxDuration: 60; // seconds

aiControlled: boolean; // AI decides when to resume

// NEW: Collage behavior during recovery

collageRecoveryMode:

\| \'pause\' // All columns pause

\| \'slowdown\' // Columns continue but slower

\| \'gentle\' // Switch to softer content temporarily

\| \'continue\'; // No change (advanced users)

textDuringRecovery: {

pool: \'recovery\'; // Use recovery affirmations

timing: \'lingering\'; // Slower display

};

}

Part 7: Arousal Auction Interface

7.1 Auction Triggers

const auctionTriggers = {

edgeNumbers: \[5, 8, 10, 13, 16, 20\],

timeIntervals: \[10, 20, 30\], // minutes

aiDetermined: {

minEdgesBetween: 3,

maxEdgesBetween: 6,

probabilityIncrease: 0.15

}

}

7.2 Auction Modal Design (Updated)

In collage mode, the auction modal appears as a center overlay that
doesn\'t fully obscure the content---keeping the visual stimulation
present while demanding a decision:

interface AuctionModalConfig {

backgroundBehavior:

\| \'freeze\' // Content pauses behind modal

\| \'dim\' // Content continues but dimmed

\| \'blur\' // Content continues but blurred

\| \'continue\'; // Full visibility (distracting by design)

hapticDuringAuction: boolean; // Keep low-level stimulation

textOverlayDuringAuction: boolean; // Keep affirmations running

decisionTimer: number \| null; // Optional countdown pressure

}

7.3 Auction Options

interface AuctionOption {

id: string;

label: string;

description: string;

commitmentType: \'edges\' \| \'denial\' \| \'lock\' \| \'content\' \|
\'task\';

commitmentValue: number \| string;

reward?: {

intensityBoost: number;

contentUnlock?: string;

hapticPattern?: string;

layoutUpgrade?: ContentLayoutMode; // NEW: Unlock better layout

};

penalty?: {

intensityDrop: number;

pauseDuration: number;

layoutDowngrade?: ContentLayoutMode; // NEW: Lose collage mode

};

}

Part 8: Goon Mode (Deep Trance)

Goon mode is an extended, deep-absorption state for users who have
demonstrated commitment (Phase 3+, 20+ sessions). It emphasizes
trance-like immersion over edge counting, and is the ideal context for
the full hypno collage experience.

8.1 Goon Mode Configuration

interface GoonModeConfig {

minDuration: 45; // minutes

maxDuration: 90; // minutes

features: {

edgeCounting: false; // No discrete edges

continuousFlow: true; // Fluid intensity

deeperContent: true; // Hypno, trance material

reducedUI: true; // Minimal controls

breathingSync: true; // Haptics sync to breath

extendedAffirmations: true; // Longer, slower text

tranceInduction: true; // Opening induction

// NEW: Collage optimizations for goon mode

defaultLayout: \'hypno\'; // Full collage + text stream

syncMode: \'cascade\'; // Hypnotic cascade effect

textTiming: \'subliminal\'; // Fast text cycling

contentIntensity: \'progressive\'; // Builds over session

};

completion: \'ai_decides\' \| \'timer\' \| \'user_signal\';

completionType: \'denial\' \| \'ruined\' \| \'full\' \| \'ai_decides\';

}

